{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Now available for iOS and OS X, SceneKit is an inventive high-level graphics framework enabling your apps to efficiently load, manipulate, and render 3D scenes. Get reintroduced to SceneKit and check out how your apps can take advantage of its latest capabilities. Learn about advanced capabilities for physics and animation, support for subdivision surfaces, new rendering effects, integration with SpriteKit, and much more."}],"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc14-609-whats-new-in-scenekit"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC14"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by reading the transcript and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC14-609-Whats-New-in-SceneKit","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"roleHeading":"WWDC14","role":"sampleCode","title":"What’s New in SceneKit"},"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"overridingTitle":"Read Transcript","isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2014\/609\/"}},"sections":[],"references":{"https://nonstrict.eu/wwdcindex/wwdc2014/609/":{"type":"download","checksum":null,"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2014\/609\/","url":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2014\/609\/"},"https://wwdcnotes